    </svg>
    
</button>

{%- assign mobel_collection = collections[section.settings.mobel_collection] -%}

{%- comment -%}
  The desktop inline nav is intentionally removed here to avoid duplicating
  the new mega-menu's own desktop navigation. The burger above opens the
  mega-menu overlay on mobile; desktop navigation is rendered inside the
  `mega-menu` section.
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- comment -%}
  Mobile popup nav removed in favor of opening the mega menu directly via the burger button.
{%- endcomment -%}

